{
  "message": "test(fuzz): add broadcast_shapes fuzz target with 12 corpus seeds\n\nAdd fuzzer for fnp-ndarray broadcasting and shape operations:\n- broadcast_shape() - shape compatibility checking\n- fix_unknown_dimension() - reshape with -1 inference\n- contiguous_strides() - C/F order stride calculation\n\nStructured corpus seeds cover edge cases:\n- Scalar shapes, 1D arrays, high-rank tensors\n- Broadcast patterns (1 vs n, shape mismatch)\n- Empty dimensions, large dimensions\n- C-order and F-order stride computation\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
